snippet.title: Dusk Diver - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Dusk Diver is a vibrant action-RPG taking place in the iconic streets of Taipei! Fight alongside guardians and utilise a unique action-orientated combat system to protect the neighbourhood from demons.

Out on PS4, Nintendo Switch & Steam:

Europe - 25th October 2019
North America - 29th October 2019

Available for Preorder Now.

http://pqube.co.uk/dusk-diver/

#DuskDiver
